{"tid":1370171,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花]到我哋中學生do 啦~~~","createTime":"2019-07-27T02:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T11:47:07.000Z","uid":271239,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"455faf9e8dafdc55f7e05354887242013ea5a751","tid":1370171,"uid":271239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:08:18.000Z","msg":"【中學生的聲音】<br />\n<br />\n我哋雖然年紀小，但都希望盡全力發出最大嘅聲音。<br />\n<br />\n學生係未來社會嘅棟樑，所以我哋都有必要為自己，為大家發聲。<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢次係香港最分化嘅一次,但亦都係香港人最團結嘅一次。而我哋中學生都想令大家更團結，所以搞咗今次嘅聯署。<br />\n<br />\n【中學生聯署計劃】<br />\n<br />\n民主運動從來都係先由中學生、大學生發起，因為我哋有一股傻勁，我哋雖然會有衝動嘅時候，但全因為我哋對未來總係抱有無限嘅理想，更願意為理想而付出。<br />\n<br />\n我哋嘅堅持已經令而家好多喺政府部門嘅大人都出咗聲啦，今次就到我哋中學生一齊集氣，比呢個不公義嘅政府聽聽，屬於香港人真正嘅聲音！<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以係表中填上你嘅學校名，同遮蓋重要個人資料嘅學生證，一齊加入聯署！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA/viewform?usp=pp_url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dpp_url&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGdx6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=0044ef53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA/viewform?usp=pp_url</a><br />\n<br />\n【A Petition from Secondary School Students for the Solidarity of All Hongkongers]<br />\n<br />\nThe voice of us:<br />\n<br />\nAlthough we are only secondary school students, we try our best to speak up. <br />\n<br />\nStudents are the future pillars of the society, and it is necessary for us to fight for the future and our next generation. <br />\n<br />\nHong Kong is now the most divided, yet Hongkongers are at the same time the most united that we have never seen before.<br />\n<br />\nWe hope we can use our power to make Hongkongers more united, so we initiate this petition.<br />\n<br />\nWe are secondary school students, we want to make the world a better place! <br />\n<br />\nPlease sign:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA/viewform?usp=pp_url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dpp_url&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGdx6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=0044ef53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdz5V_o8_YiWRVqSsNi9tP1abAHkU0cd7TYr69r1wO1_GyFSA/viewform?usp=pp_url</a>"},{"pid":"ba489e1c1aed6ce26c417fe826e04305dda06c7e","tid":1370171,"uid":290792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:16:10.000Z","msg":"中學生push"},{"pid":"b45a528af345754d9a09fcddd5f9a3e271b7e960","tid":1370171,"uid":289451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:31:47.000Z","msg":"YC人push <br />\n但我下年個學年先係，未有學生證<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31dcc984a55293cd13b930a6f058827d6e061f60","tid":1370171,"uid":236646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c651e1fd648134ea870ceb37fadf407bfbed47a8","tid":1370171,"uid":28870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25efb960bc26ce89f4b47ddad150a71b928d4976","tid":1370171,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:30:58.000Z","msg":"我認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"